Dialogue: 10,0:01:42.68,0:01:44.39,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sial, mereka tidak ada habisnya!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:44.47,0:01:45.43,dialog,,0,0,0,,Cepat!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:45.89,0:01:47.23,dialog,,0,0,0,,Di sekitar sudut ini!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:49.90,0:01:52.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mereka benar-benar keluar\Ndari Arc de Triomphe.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:52.73,0:01:53.57,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hei!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:53.65,0:01:55.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,Cari orang yang menebarkan kelopak bunga!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:55.69,0:01:57.49,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tunggu, kita ketahuan.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:57.57,0:01:58.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mereka menyerang kita!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:59.03,0:01:59.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mundur!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:00.03,0:02:01.53,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mundur, sekarang!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:04.33,0:02:07.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hanya itu rekaman yang kita punya.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:07.16,0:02:08.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Omong-omong,
Dialogue: 10,0:02:08.08,0:02:12.29,dialog,,0,0,0,,aku meminta Phone menganalisis\Ndan memprediksi kehidupan lampau mereka,
Dialogue: 10,0:02:12.38,0:02:14.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,tapi dia mencapai kesimpulan\Nyang sama dengan Tim Analisis kita.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:15.05,0:02:16.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pertama, yang ada di rekaman\Nadalah Napoleon.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:17.47,0:02:19.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bakatnya adalah "Dorong Kaisar Agung".
Dialogue: 10,0:02:19.76,0:02:21.72,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kenapa di Arc de Triomphe?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:21.80,0:02:23.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa itu keinginan yang tertinggal\Ndari kehidupan lampaunya?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:23.47,0:02:27.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,Di bawah Arc de Triomphe\Nada makam Perang Dunia I.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:28.10,0:02:32.19,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tampaknya bakatnya memanggil orang mati\Ndan memaksa mereka bertarung.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:32.69,0:02:34.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sepertinya bukan ancaman besar.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:35.23,0:02:38.32,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi kita tidak bisa\Nmenembakkan misil di sana.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:38.57,0:02:40.07,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jadi, apa rencananya?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:40.16,0:02:42.07,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa kita akan melewatkan target ini?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:42.70,0:02:44.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kita tidak punya pilihan untuk saat ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:44.62,0:02:47.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau begitu,\Nkita harus menargetkan yang di laut dahulu.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:48.46,0:02:50.12,dialog,,0,0,0,,Rachel Carson.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:50.21,0:02:52.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bakatnya adalah "Biru Sunyi".
Dialogue: 10,0:02:53.17,0:02:55.38,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pengembali tersesat ini merepotkan.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:55.46,0:02:58.42,dialog,,0,0,0,,Karena dia di laut,\Nhanya sedikit laporan saksi mata.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:58.51,0:03:01.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sulit melacak pergerakannya dengan akurat.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:01.43,0:03:02.26,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tunggu...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:02.34,0:03:05.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lagi pula,\Nkau dan laut tidak cocok, Einstein.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:06.93,0:03:08.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa boleh buat.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:09.85,0:03:12.56,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bagaimana dengan yang di Menara Elizabeth?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:14.44,0:03:15.32,dialog,,0,0,0,,Laplace.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:15.40,0:03:17.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bakat mereka adalah "Monster Laplace".
Dialogue: 10,0:03:18.03,0:03:18.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,Maxwell.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:18.99,0:03:21.32,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bakat mereka adalah "Iblis Maxwell".
Dialogue: 10,0:03:21.78,0:03:22.78,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kurasa yang ini juga sulit.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:22.87,0:03:24.07,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hei!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:24.32,0:03:26.37,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jangan marah!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:26.45,0:03:28.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,Meski kita merekam Pengembali ini di kamera,
Dialogue: 10,0:03:28.58,0:03:30.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,tidak ada catatan saksi mata sungguhan.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:30.58,0:03:32.46,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa? Bagaimana mungkin?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:32.79,0:03:34.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,"Monster Laplace"...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:34.17,0:03:38.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,bisa melihat kebenaran\Ndi balik semua konvergensi.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:38.30,0:03:39.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,"Iblis Maxwell"
Dialogue: 10,0:03:39.63,0:03:42.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,bisa melihat pergerakan molekul.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:42.43,0:03:43.64,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sederhananya,
Dialogue: 10,0:03:43.72,0:03:45.43,dialog,,0,0,0,,selama mereka tidak ingin terlihat,
Dialogue: 10,0:03:45.51,0:03:48.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,mereka adalah Pengembali\Nyang hampir mustahil untuk ditemui.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:48.10,0:03:50.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lalu kenapa? Apa itu artinya kita\Ntidak bisa menghadapi mereka?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:50.56,0:03:51.89,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sudah, tenanglah.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:51.98,0:03:54.23,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku juga mencari target yang cocok.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:56.02,0:04:00.57,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau begitu, gunakan senjata kalian\Nuntuk dekatkan Pengembali liar kepadaku...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:00.65,0:04:02.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dari sudut pandangku,\Nsebenarnya itu cukup mengejutkan.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:03.86,0:04:06.83,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau sangat antusias memburu Pengembali liar.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:06.91,0:04:11.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mungkinkah kau tersentuh dengan\Ncara dewasaku dalam menangani masalah?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:11.08,0:04:12.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,Karena Ein yang lama
Dialogue: 10,0:04:12.50,0:04:15.17,dialog,,0,0,0,,akan bertindak murni karena impulsif.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:16.96,0:04:19.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tentu saja, aku mengkhawatirkan Musashi.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:19.80,0:04:22.63,dialog,,0,0,0,,Namun, menemukan Benih\Nadalah prioritas utama kita.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:23.76,0:04:26.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bisa dibilang Benih adalah\Njantung dari semua Pengembali.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:27.47,0:04:28.97,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jika jatuh ke tangan manusia,
Dialogue: 10,0:04:29.06,0:04:30.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,para Pengembali akan musnah.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:30.97,0:04:32.56,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jika jatuh ke tangan Hutan Para Legenda,
Dialogue: 10,0:04:32.64,0:04:34.77,dialog,,0,0,0,,manusia akan kehilangan cahayanya.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:35.44,0:04:38.44,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi bagaimana jika aku mendapatkannya?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:38.52,0:04:42.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu akan menjadi kekuatan ketiga\Nyang mampu bernegosiasi setara
Dialogue: 10,0:04:42.74,0:04:44.53,dialog,,0,0,0,,dengan Hutan Para Legenda dan manusia.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:45.20,0:04:47.24,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jika dipakai, bisa bangun keseimbangan.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:47.32,0:04:49.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu menjadi solusi selain
Dialogue: 10,0:04:49.28,0:04:52.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,memusnahkan Pengembali atau manusia.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:52.58,0:04:55.37,dialog,,0,0,0,,Newton akan melakukan hal yang sama.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:55.46,0:04:57.46,dialog,,0,0,0,,- Bagaimana ini bisa terjadi?\N- Cari para penyintas.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:58.13,0:04:59.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,Cari mereka yang belum dikendalikan.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:00.59,0:05:02.17,dialog,,0,0,0,,Cari rekan-rekanmu!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:02.26,0:05:03.97,dialog,,0,0,0,,Namaku Newton.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:04.05,0:05:06.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku diperintahkan menjadi asistenmu.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:08.10,0:05:11.22,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kenapa aku harus menghabiskan hari liburku\Nyang langka bersama si Kepala Apel ini?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:11.64,0:05:13.39,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sebenarnya aku cukup bahagia.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:13.48,0:05:15.44,dialog,,0,0,0,,Rasanya seperti bepergian bersamamu.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:18.31,0:05:20.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa tujuanmu?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:20.82,0:05:22.53,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kenapa kau bergabung\Ndengan Hutan Para Legenda?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:23.32,0:05:25.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,Akan kuberi tahu suatu hari nanti.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:25.28,0:05:26.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,Suatu hari nanti...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:29.58,0:05:31.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,Saat pria itu kembali,
Dialogue: 10,0:05:31.66,0:05:35.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,aku harus menciptakan situasi saat\Nmasih ada ruang untuk bermanuver.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:36.00,0:05:39.54,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi menurut kami,\Nantusiasme adalah hal yang baik.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:40.50,0:05:43.59,dialog,,0,0,0,,Omong-omong,\Nberapa jangkauan teleportasi spasialmu?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:43.67,0:05:45.97,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku bisa teleportasi ke tempat\Nyang pernah kudatangi.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:46.47,0:05:49.39,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pada dasarnya aku sudah\Nmendaftarkan semua ibu kota dunia.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:50.01,0:05:53.39,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau begitu, prosesnya akan seperti ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:53.77,0:05:56.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,Satu. Teleportasi ke sisi target.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:56.89,0:05:59.94,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dua. Kitazuka dan Unit Sudut Hitam\Nakan melumpuhkan mereka.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:00.02,0:06:03.69,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tiga. Ambil Cabang\Ndan teleportasi ke markas.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:03.78,0:06:07.78,dialog,,0,0,0,,Empat. Ulangi sampai kita\Nmendapatkan jumlah target Cabang.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:07.86,0:06:11.37,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa? Kau berencana mengalahkan\Npara Pengembali sendirian?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:11.45,0:06:12.83,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jangan konyol.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:12.91,0:06:14.83,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sudah kubilang aku akan menangani semuanya.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:15.08,0:06:16.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,Berhentilah berlagak tangguh.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:17.12,0:06:18.92,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau baru saja pulih.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:19.00,0:06:21.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,Teleportasi sekali saja pasti melelahkan.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:22.34,0:06:25.34,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lagi pula, ini pertarungan umat manusia.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:25.42,0:06:28.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bawahanku luar biasa, belum lagi diriku.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:28.55,0:06:31.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mereka juga butuh pengalaman bertarung\Nmelawan Pengembali.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:31.39,0:06:34.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kami sudah lama siap untuk berkorban.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:34.26,0:06:35.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lagi pula,
Dialogue: 10,0:06:35.68,0:06:38.23,dialog,,0,0,0,,kita punya cara lain.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:38.31,0:06:39.69,dialog,,0,0,0,,- Benar, bukan?\N- Ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:40.02,0:06:41.73,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sepertinya mereka tiba tepat waktu.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:43.02,0:06:45.69,dialog,,0,0,0,,Baik, aku akan membuka pintunya sekarang.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:46.86,0:06:47.78,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:48.74,0:06:49.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pengembali?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:49.99,0:06:50.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kenapa?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:51.20,0:06:53.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ini semua bagian dari rencana Kouu.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:53.53,0:06:57.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mereka Pengembali yang sengaja tertangkap,\Nseperti Nostradamus.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:57.87,0:06:59.46,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mereka tidak mau bicara sebelumnya,
Dialogue: 10,0:06:59.54,0:07:02.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,tapi begitu aku menyebutkan detailnya,\Nmereka mengakui semuanya.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:02.96,0:07:06.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku hanya tidak menduga\Nhampir semuanya sengaja tertangkap.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:07.84,0:07:11.22,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kami adalah pedang kedua\Nyang dipilih oleh Kouu.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:11.30,0:07:12.89,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pedang Warisan!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:13.43,0:07:15.89,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ini permintaan mendiang teman.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:15.97,0:07:17.93,dialog,,0,0,0,,Biarkan kami membantu dalam pertempuran ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:18.27,0:07:20.23,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku Götz "Tangan Besi"
Dialogue: 10,0:07:20.31,0:07:21.73,dialog,,0,0,0,,Berlichingen.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:31.78,0:07:32.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:32.87,0:07:34.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,Begini...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:34.66,0:07:35.74,dialog,,0,0,0,,Siapa kau?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:35.83,0:07:38.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ingatan Tangan Besi tua itu makin memburuk.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:39.12,0:07:40.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,- Apa?\N- Lo?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:40.66,0:07:41.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku juga tidak mengenalnya.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:42.04,0:07:43.83,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ada yang mengenalnya?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:49.30,0:07:50.92,dialog,,0,0,0,,Siapa kau?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:51.68,0:07:53.39,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sepertinya kau bukan Pengembali.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:54.85,0:07:56.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:57.39,0:07:58.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,Begini...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:59.06,0:08:02.73,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jika melewati hutan dan mengikuti sungai,\Nkita akan tiba di laut.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:03.19,0:08:05.27,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sepertinya ke arah sana.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:05.36,0:08:06.19,dialog,,0,0,0,,Begitu rupanya.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:06.48,0:08:08.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,Entah kenapa, aku merasa sangat menyesal.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:08.23,0:08:09.57,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak perlu minta maaf.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:09.65,0:08:12.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mari bicara setelah kita menemukan Musashi.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:15.20,0:08:16.24,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ada apa?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:16.33,0:08:17.28,dialog,,0,0,0,,Keluar!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:17.37,0:08:19.49,dialog,,0,0,0,,Atau aku akan menebangmu sekalian\Ndengan pohon ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:23.83,0:08:26.46,dialog,,0,0,0,,Maaf.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:26.54,0:08:28.13,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tidak berniat melawanmu.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:28.21,0:08:29.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,Siapa dia?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:29.59,0:08:30.63,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sebutkan namamu.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:30.71,0:08:32.22,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jika kau tidak bekerja sama...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:33.13,0:08:34.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:36.72,0:08:38.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,Membosankan sekali.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:38.81,0:08:40.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hei, Apel Kecil.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:40.43,0:08:41.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,Astaga.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:41.89,0:08:44.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bukankah kau akan\Nmemberi Einstein pelajaran?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:45.27,0:08:47.94,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak, aku memang sudah pergi...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:49.44,0:08:50.82,dialog,,0,0,0,,Persembunyian.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:51.49,0:08:54.03,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau tertipu dengan informasi palsu, bukan?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:54.70,0:08:57.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,Neumann tidak sepenuhnya\Ndikendalikan, bukan?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:58.03,0:09:00.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia melawan sekuat tenaga\Ndi kedalaman kesadarannya.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:00.99,0:09:02.54,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia sangat tangguh.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:02.83,0:09:03.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,Astaga.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:03.79,0:09:05.54,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ada apa?\NBahkan Tesla seperti ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:05.96,0:09:07.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sama seperti Albert.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:07.92,0:09:09.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,Haruskah kusebut membosankan?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:09.63,0:09:10.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tak bisa termotivasi.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:11.38,0:09:16.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bahkan Edison, yang biasa berdebat denganku,\Nmenjadi sangat lamban.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:16.39,0:09:18.64,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mungkin karena "penaklukan" makin dalam.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:18.72,0:09:20.56,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia seperti boneka sekarang.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:20.97,0:09:22.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,Yang lainnya sama saja.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:23.06,0:09:24.52,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jadi...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:24.98,0:09:27.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,Haruskah kita memulai\NRencana Umat Manusia Agung lebih awal?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:28.40,0:09:31.44,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pengisian daya sudah selesai.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:31.53,0:09:33.69,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pemandangan planet yang hancur
Dialogue: 10,0:09:33.78,0:09:35.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,seharusnya cukup menghibur.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:36.61,0:09:38.53,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau cukup tidak sabar.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:38.62,0:09:41.87,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mari kita lihat dan nikmati kebosanan ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:42.49,0:09:46.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kita mengeluarkan deklarasi perang,\Nmembuat umat manusia kacau.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:46.58,0:09:48.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,Alih-alih bersatu, negara-negara
Dialogue: 10,0:09:48.42,0:09:50.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,sibuk saling mengawasi,\Nkarena takut dan curiga.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:51.21,0:09:55.13,dialog,,0,0,0,,Para Pengembali yang kita lepaskan\Njuga menyebarkan kelopak bunga.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:55.22,0:09:58.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dunia memang mulai miring.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:59.34,0:10:02.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku juga tidak suka merasa bosan.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:02.60,0:10:04.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ada apa dengan pria ini?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:07.81,0:10:09.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia wajah baru.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:09.40,0:10:10.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dari mana asalmu?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:11.23,0:10:13.03,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau sekutu baru kami?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:21.24,0:10:22.53,dialog,,0,0,0,,Nightingale?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:22.62,0:10:24.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jangan mendekat, Albert.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:24.24,0:10:27.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kristal itu akan menghancurkan segalanya.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:27.37,0:10:28.87,dialog,,0,0,0,,Maaf.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:28.96,0:10:31.54,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku terlalu bersemangat.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:34.96,0:10:38.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku sudah menunggumu muncul.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:38.93,0:10:41.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,Karena kau di sini, izinkan aku bertanya.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:41.97,0:10:43.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,Boleh aku tahu namamu?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:44.01,0:10:45.56,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:47.06,0:10:47.89,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku
Dialogue: 10,0:10:47.98,0:10:50.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,Alan Smithee.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:52.40,0:10:54.57,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku Alan Smithee,
Dialogue: 10,0:10:54.65,0:10:56.99,dialog,,0,0,0,,pencipta Cabang Reinkarnasi.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:57.07,0:10:58.49,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mari berbincang.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:59.07,0:11:01.03,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pencipta Cabang?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:01.11,0:11:02.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,Benarkah?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:02.24,0:11:03.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,Semuanya, jangan bergerak.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:04.24,0:11:06.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau, mundur dan rekam semuanya.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:08.00,0:11:09.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sayang sekali.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:09.41,0:11:12.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalian selalu lapar seperti bayi burung.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:12.84,0:11:17.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sepertinya aku agak berlebihan dengan\NCabang yang kubagikan dengan bebas.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:17.97,0:11:21.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sepertinya kalian semua memilih kehancuran.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:21.13,0:11:24.47,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tahu hari ini akan datang,
Dialogue: 10,0:11:24.56,0:11:26.64,dialog,,0,0,0,,tapi aku masih merasa agak ragu.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:27.35,0:11:28.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau mengerti, bukan?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:28.93,0:11:29.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,Seperti kata pepatah,
Dialogue: 10,0:11:29.89,0:11:32.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,"Anak yang kurang pandai\Njustru lebih disayang."
Dialogue: 10,0:11:32.69,0:11:36.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,Meski begitu,\Naku menghormati pilihan kalian.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:36.69,0:11:40.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ini akan menjadi percakapan terakhir kita.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:41.15,0:11:43.37,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ada kata-kata terakhir?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:43.45,0:11:45.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,Atau mungkin doa untuk diucapkan?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:45.95,0:11:47.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sekarang, mari bicara.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:47.74,0:11:49.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tanpa menahan apa pun.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:49.33,0:11:52.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,Agar kalian, yang menuju kehancuran,\Ntidak akan menyesal.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:53.54,0:11:55.09,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa yang dia bicarakan?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:55.92,0:11:58.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pria ini... menciptakan Cabang Reinkarnasi?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:59.59,0:12:00.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,Benarkah...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:01.88,0:12:02.93,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jika itu benar...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:03.01,0:12:03.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,Touya.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:03.93,0:12:04.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:04.85,0:12:06.97,dialog,,0,0,0,,- Nona Yagyu?\N- Jangan hanya berdiri di sana. Ayo!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:10.39,0:12:12.69,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kita sedang terburu-buru.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:12.77,0:12:15.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kita tidak punya waktu untuk pembohong.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:15.11,0:12:17.44,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu juga bisa menjadi taktik mengulur waktu\Noleh Hutan Para Legenda.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:17.52,0:12:18.57,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak, tapi...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:19.03,0:12:20.32,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tunggu sebentar!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:23.53,0:12:26.28,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku mahatahu.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:26.37,0:12:29.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kehancuran tiga bulan dari sekarang\Nsudah ditakdirkan.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:30.83,0:12:34.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidakkah kau ingin setidaknya\Nmenemukan ketenangan pikiran?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:35.08,0:12:38.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bekas luka yang ditinggalkan\Npengkhianat pasti sakit.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:38.84,0:12:41.38,dialog,,0,0,0,,Atau masih berdenyut?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:41.47,0:12:43.09,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mata kirimu itu.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:44.80,0:12:46.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sudah kubilang kami terburu-buru!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:50.02,0:12:50.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:51.43,0:12:53.64,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku belum pernah mendengar nama itu.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:53.73,0:12:55.56,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa ada Legenda dengan nama itu?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:55.73,0:12:57.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,Namanya "Pseudonim".
Dialogue: 10,0:12:57.94,0:12:59.78,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mungkin itu lelucon kecilnya sendiri.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:00.19,0:13:02.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa dia temanmu?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:02.19,0:13:03.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sayangnya,
Dialogue: 10,0:13:03.53,0:13:05.99,dialog,,0,0,0,,aku tidak pernah bisa berteman dengannya.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:06.66,0:13:10.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi keberadaannya sesuai dugaanku.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:10.24,0:13:13.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau pernah dengar paradoks ayam dan telur?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:13.46,0:13:17.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,Maksudmu debat "mana yang lebih dahulu,\Nayam atau telur"?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:17.29,0:13:19.13,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa hubungannya dengan dia?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:19.21,0:13:21.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku sudah memikirkannya.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:22.71,0:13:25.22,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kapan Pengembali pertama lahir?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:25.97,0:13:28.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu pertanyaan yang berbeda.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:28.10,0:13:34.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dilema sebab-akibat hanya bekerja ketika\Nsebab dan akibat membentuk lingkaran.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:34.39,0:13:36.27,dialog,,0,0,0,,Manusia menjadi Pengembali,
Dialogue: 10,0:13:36.35,0:13:38.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,tapi Pengembali tidak menjadi manusia.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:39.11,0:13:40.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,Benar sekali.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:40.90,0:13:44.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jadi, kapan Pengembali pertama muncul?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:44.19,0:13:46.32,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tak ada yang tahu.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:46.41,0:13:50.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,Karena Pengembali kehilangan ingatan\Ndari sebelum mereka berubah.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:50.66,0:13:54.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,Meski begitu,\NPengembali terus lahir di seluruh dunia.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:55.50,0:13:57.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,Cabang Reinkarnasi
Dialogue: 10,0:13:57.58,0:13:59.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,adalah sesuatu yang diberikan kepada kita.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:00.79,0:14:05.42,dialog,,0,0,0,,Oleh makhluk hiper-dimensi\Nyang tak bisa tinggal dalam ingatan.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:05.51,0:14:08.09,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tidak pernah mengira akan\Nmelihatnya dengan mataku sendiri.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:08.68,0:14:13.47,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kini kita menyaksikan\Nmomen terakhir umat manusia.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:13.56,0:14:15.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,Karena kau muncul secara langsung,
Dialogue: 10,0:14:15.89,0:14:18.94,dialog,,0,0,0,,itu artinya rencanaku pasti akan berhasil!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:20.44,0:14:22.32,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sayang sekali.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:22.40,0:14:25.19,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak kusangka aku akan\Nmerindukan kesenangan seperti ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:25.53,0:14:26.49,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pinjami aku pisaumu.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:26.57,0:14:28.07,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa? Tapi Kapten,
Dialogue: 10,0:14:28.16,0:14:29.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,kau bilang jangan bergerak...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:29.28,0:14:30.49,dialog,,0,0,0,,Diam dan berikan saja kepadaku!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:30.57,0:14:31.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,Baik.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:33.54,0:14:34.79,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hei, Berengsek.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:34.87,0:14:36.79,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau bilang ingin bicara, kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:36.87,0:14:38.46,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau begitu, mari bicara.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:38.54,0:14:39.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,Benih itu ada atau tidak?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:40.04,0:14:41.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ada.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:41.29,0:14:42.13,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mau lihat?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:44.67,0:14:45.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa yang terjadi?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:49.72,0:14:51.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sepertinya aku bisa melihat sesuatu.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:52.80,0:14:54.22,dialog,,0,0,0,,Cabang tumbuh darinya.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:55.56,0:14:57.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu "Benih Reinkarnasi"...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:59.94,0:15:01.52,dialog,,0,0,0,,Intuisiku memberitahuku
Dialogue: 10,0:15:01.90,0:15:04.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,tidak boleh melupakan momen ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:05.48,0:15:06.57,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tidak boleh lupa!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:08.03,0:15:09.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,Begitu banyak Cabang Reinkarnasi...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:11.53,0:15:13.12,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau memang energik.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:13.45,0:15:15.79,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia tidak terluka setelah serangan langsung.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:15.87,0:15:18.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,Nona Yagyu, tolong singkirkan pedangmu.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:18.16,0:15:20.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau percaya dia pencipta Cabang?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:21.29,0:15:23.17,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tidak punya pilihan selain percaya.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:29.34,0:15:31.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku bersikap seolah-olah\Nsemua akan baik-baik saja,
Dialogue: 10,0:15:32.47,0:15:35.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,tapi semua itu bisa hancur\Nkarena Hutan Para Legenda.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:36.10,0:15:39.89,dialog,,0,0,0,,Namun, jika kita bisa dapatkan informasi\Ndari pencipta Cabang,
Dialogue: 10,0:15:39.98,0:15:41.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,situasinya akan berubah.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:41.69,0:15:42.94,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa yang akan kau tanyakan?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:43.36,0:15:45.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,"Apa Benih Reinkarnasi itu ada?"
Dialogue: 10,0:15:45.77,0:15:48.82,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sangat penting jika kita punya cara\Nuntuk menghentikan Hutan Para Legenda.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:49.61,0:15:52.24,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jika kita bisa tahu darinya\Ndi mana Benih itu,
Dialogue: 10,0:15:53.12,0:15:56.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,kita bisa mencegah lahirnya\Nlebih banyak Legenda.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:56.58,0:15:58.54,dialog,,0,0,0,,Haruskah kukatakan ini sudah diduga?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:59.20,0:16:02.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku terkesan dia membaca situasi\Ndalam waktu singkat.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:04.42,0:16:07.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sampai tadi, Musashi seharusnya\Nmenjadi perhatian utamanya.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:09.34,0:16:12.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,Namun, dia masih memprioritaskan\Nmenghentikan Hutan Para Legenda?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:13.76,0:16:16.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mengetahui dirinya\Ndalam posisi tanpa harapan,
Dialogue: 10,0:16:16.18,0:16:18.97,dialog,,0,0,0,,dia tetap terlalu realistis dan pragmatis.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:19.06,0:16:20.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bagaimana dia bisa tetap tenang?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:21.35,0:16:23.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kenapa orang seperti dia menjadi Pengembali?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:25.02,0:16:27.07,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jika dia benar-benar mahatahu...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:27.86,0:16:28.69,dialog,,0,0,0,,Maka aku...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:29.32,0:16:30.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jika itu aku...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:30.74,0:16:32.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,Serakah sekali.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:32.28,0:16:34.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,Menginginkan sesuatu yang sudah kau buang.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:35.28,0:16:38.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,Baiklah. Silakan ingat.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:38.16,0:16:39.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bersama semua kebencian itu.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:46.08,0:16:46.92,dialog,,0,0,0,,Siapa itu?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:47.13,0:16:48.46,dialog,,0,0,0,,Siapa yang menangis?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:49.46,0:16:50.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ini...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:51.51,0:16:52.93,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tidak akan pernah lupa...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:53.01,0:16:54.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa itu aku?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:55.55,0:16:58.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tak akan melupakanmu,\Natau rasa sakit ini!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:04.06,0:17:05.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kelopak bunga...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:07.48,0:17:08.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mungkinkah...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:08.94,0:17:09.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,kau...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:15.86,0:17:17.12,dialog,,0,0,0,,Musashi.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:20.33,0:17:21.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Nona Yagyu?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:22.87,0:17:25.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,Nona Yagyu!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:25.17,0:17:26.04,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ada apa?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:26.12,0:17:27.13,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau tiba-tiba pingsan.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:27.46,0:17:28.29,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:28.63,0:17:30.63,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa yang kita lakukan?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:32.13,0:17:33.17,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lo?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:33.26,0:17:35.26,dialog,,0,0,0,,Satu jam sudah berlalu.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:36.64,0:17:37.47,dialog,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:38.39,0:17:39.43,dialog,,0,0,0,,Benih itu ada!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:39.51,0:17:41.14,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hei, kau dengar?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:42.10,0:17:42.93,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tunggu sebentar.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:43.02,0:17:44.77,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kitazuka, tanganmu!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:46.81,0:17:50.32,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku merasa seperti bicara dengan seseorang.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:51.15,0:17:53.32,dialog,,0,0,0,,"Dia" mahatahu.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:53.40,0:17:56.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku mengajukan pertanyaan\Nyang bisa mematahkan status quo.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:57.16,0:17:59.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lalu aku mendengar jawabannya.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:00.03,0:18:04.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,Rasanya seperti percakapan panjang,\Ntapi juga seperti percakapan singkat.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:05.41,0:18:07.17,dialog,,0,0,0,,Meski terdengar seperti mimpi,
Dialogue: 10,0:18:07.62,0:18:10.04,dialog,,0,0,0,,anehnya, kurasa itu bukan...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:20.10,0:18:21.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku akan tidur.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:21.76,0:18:23.14,dialog,,0,0,0,,Nightingale?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:23.22,0:18:28.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,Waktu kosong ini adalah kunci\Napakah keinginanku akan terkabul.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:29.48,0:18:34.07,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi di saat bersamaan,\Nkekhawatiran sia-sia muncul.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:34.99,0:18:37.49,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku harus mengambil ekor yang hilang.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:38.61,0:18:43.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,Selama waktu ini, tolong hindari kontak\Ndengan Einstein dan yang lainnya.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:55.96,0:18:58.59,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau sudah sadar, Nona Yagyu?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:58.68,0:18:59.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau baik-baik saja?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:59.93,0:19:01.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau tahu di mana kita?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:01.60,0:19:02.43,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:02.93,0:19:04.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku baik-baik saja.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:04.56,0:19:06.89,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau mengerang, jadi, aku khawatir.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:07.89,0:19:09.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau sudah membuat kontak?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:09.56,0:19:10.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:10.69,0:19:13.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mereka bilang sudah\Nmemastikan keberadaan Benih.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:13.11,0:19:16.07,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dan sesuatu tentang Pria Tanpa Wajah.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:16.40,0:19:18.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sejujurnya, aku benar-benar bingung.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:18.82,0:19:19.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,Benar-benar bingung?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:20.20,0:19:21.28,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau tidak ingat?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:21.74,0:19:22.62,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:22.70,0:19:23.53,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ingat apa?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:23.87,0:19:25.79,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bukankah kau bicara dengan Alan?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:25.87,0:19:26.87,dialog,,0,0,0,,Alan?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:27.29,0:19:28.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,Siapa itu?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:29.25,0:19:30.46,dialog,,0,0,0,,Begitu rupanya.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:31.12,0:19:32.46,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jadi, begitu.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:37.01,0:19:38.13,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku mengerti.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:39.05,0:19:41.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa itu artinya aku harus melakukannya?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:41.55,0:19:42.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,Nona Yagyu?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:43.14,0:19:44.56,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau baik-baik saja?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:44.64,0:19:46.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bukan itu intinya.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:46.39,0:19:47.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku merasa luar biasa sekarang.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:48.56,0:19:51.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku belum pernah merasa sebaik ini\Nsejak menjadi Pengembali.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:53.11,0:19:54.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ayo percepat.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:56.90,0:19:58.94,dialog,,0,0,0,,Nona Yagyu.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:59.03,0:20:00.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,Haruskah kita istirahat?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:00.99,0:20:02.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hari mulai gelap.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:03.87,0:20:05.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:05.28,0:20:08.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia tak akan berhenti apa pun ucapanku,\Ndan dia bahkan tidak menjawabku.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:08.75,0:20:10.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ada apa dengannya?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:10.33,0:20:11.79,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lihat, kita sudah sampai.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:14.29,0:20:16.09,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa ini kuil terbengkalai?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:16.80,0:20:18.59,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lihat betapa bobroknya ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:19.46,0:20:21.72,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tunggu, Nona Yagyu, ada apa?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:22.43,0:20:23.72,dialog,,0,0,0,,Nona Yagyu!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:27.06,0:20:28.52,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tunggu!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:37.32,0:20:39.07,dialog,,0,0,0,,Haito?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:39.74,0:20:41.03,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tou... ya...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:41.11,0:20:42.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,Syukurlah.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:42.45,0:20:44.78,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kami datang untuk menjemputmu.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:45.57,0:20:47.24,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa yang terjadi padanya?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:47.91,0:20:49.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sama seperti dahulu.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:51.41,0:20:52.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku ingin bicara baik-baik denganmu...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:52.58,0:20:53.42,dialog,,0,0,0,,Maafkan aku.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:53.50,0:20:54.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:54.42,0:20:56.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tidak bisa bertarung lagi.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:58.59,0:21:00.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ayahku sudah meninggal.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:00.92,0:21:02.97,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia sudah lama meninggal di sini.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:04.55,0:21:07.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tujuan yang mendorongku mengejar bakatku
Dialogue: 10,0:21:07.43,0:21:08.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,sudah hilang sekarang.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:10.27,0:21:12.39,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku bodoh sekali.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:13.31,0:21:15.44,dialog,,0,0,0,,Andai aku tak mengejar bakat...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:15.52,0:21:17.52,dialog,,0,0,0,,Andai aku tetap di sisinya...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:18.77,0:21:20.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,Haito, apa yang terjadi?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:20.98,0:21:24.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sepertinya kau juga sudah bertemu\Ndengan Pria Tanpa Wajah itu.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:26.41,0:21:29.03,dialog,,0,0,0,,Karena kau sudah kehilangan semangat hidup,
Dialogue: 10,0:21:29.12,0:21:30.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,kau tak keberatan
Dialogue: 10,0:21:30.41,0:21:32.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,jika kupenggal, kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:32.83,0:21:34.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,Nona Yagyu?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:34.25,0:21:35.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa maksudmu?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:36.08,0:21:38.92,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa ketidakmampuanku membuatmu marah?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:39.00,0:21:42.17,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jika itu bisa meredakan\Nkemarahanmu, ambillah.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:47.22,0:21:48.43,dialog,,0,0,0,,Nona Yagyu!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:48.51,0:21:49.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa yang kau lakukan?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:49.97,0:21:51.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,Haito!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:51.18,0:21:52.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,Meredakan kemarahanku?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:52.68,0:21:54.73,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau baru saja bilang\N"meredakan kemarahanku", bukan?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:55.69,0:21:58.44,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau begitu, aku tidak akan menahan diri.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:58.52,0:22:01.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bersiaplah untuk menderita!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:02.11,0:22:03.32,dialog,,0,0,0,,Nona Yagyu!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:36.62,0:23:37.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bakat yang robek.
